reviews.comment: Very lightweight, comfortable, and supportive. I had the cute heeled nursing clogs but at the end of my clinical rotation my feet were killing me, so I ordered a few pairs of all white sneakers on amazon and these were the most comfortable out of them all. I will admit that they aren't super duper stylish, but I am not wearing them out on the town, and for the hard hospital floors, they keep my feet (and back) from hurting...I have recommended these to the other classes at my school
